summary: UNISWAP - Once upon a time, in the chaotic land of blockchain, there was a simple, round little character named Numpty. He wasn’t the sharpest tool in the shed, but that never stopped him from dreaming big. While others were busy creating complex algorithms and revolutionary technology, Numpty had a different idea. Why not create a coin that’s as unpredictable and fun as he is? And so, Numpty Coin was born. Why be smart when you can be Numpty? Foolproof fun, powered by Numpty!
